ync" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SabrinaCarpenterDollyParton-collaboration-Please-Please-Please.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SabrinaCarpenterDollyParton-collaboration-Please-Please-Please-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SabrinaCarpenterDollyParton-collaboration-Please-Please-Please-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SabrinaCarpenterDollyParton-collaboration-Please-Please-Please-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SabrinaCarpenterDollyParton-collaboration-Please-Please-Please-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SabrinaCarpenterDollyParton-collaboration-Please-Please-Please-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton</a> ）共享了一个新的合作版本“请请请请请”  - 在下面听它。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Sabrina Carpenter  - “ Short N&#39;Sweet”评论：新的流行公主上升</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手与Country Icon合作，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-deluxe-version-of-short-n-sweet-featuring-dolly-parton-3834745">Carpenter的最新专辑“ Short N&#39;Sweet”的豪华版</a>中获得了联合新鲜单曲，该单曲今天发行（2月14日）。</p><p> “多莉和我在皮卡车唱歌！！！！” Carpenter在社交媒体上写道，同时分享了经过改进的曲目。 “我很荣幸能拥有我最大的偶像之一，这对我来说意义重大。 &#39;Short N&#39;Sweet&#39;Deluxe现在已经出来了！去看听听！！！”</p><p>她补充说：“永远爱你@dollyparton <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f90d.png" alt="🤍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f98b.png" alt="🦋" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 。”</p><p>该协作带有黑白官方视频，其中两人一起开放式道路。当木匠带轮时，他们交易人声，帕顿坐在乘客座位上。</p><p>有一次，我们看到在二人车被警车追赶之前，有很多现金从皮卡中飞出。然后，相机向一个男人抚摸着一个男人，后者在他的头上绑着一个袋子。在这里调整： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sabrina Carpenter-请请ft。DollyParton" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YiQ7qiL73aI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGCnJwgu40b/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.