2月14日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>除了“请请请”返工之外，``Short N&#39;Sweet&#39;&#39;的豪华版还包含奖金曲目“ 15分钟”，“不能使它变得更加困难”，“忙碌的女人”和“不好的评论”。在这里通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spotify</a>听： </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：短N＆apos;甜（豪华）" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/3WzBIQmn2hrulLeTY9smkk?si=4X_WqiPYSlO0mc31gYR0Tw&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>原始版本的“请请请”在英国和美国排名第一。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854">它最近在2025年格莱美奖上被提名为年度歌曲</a>，但最终输给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-not-like-us-streams-jump-by-430-per-cent-after-super-bowl-performance-3836793">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）的“不喜欢我们”</a> 。</p><p>但是，卡彭特（Carpenter）在当晚确实获得了两个奖项：最佳流行独奏表演（“浓缩咖啡”）和最佳流行声音专辑（&#39;Short N&#39;Sweet&#39;）。</p><p>同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-sabrina-carpenter-confirmed-to-perform-3836811">这位歌手将在下个月的2025年Brits 2025上表演</a>，她将获得享有声望的全球成功奖。此外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">她还参加了年度国际艺术家和年度国际歌曲（“浓缩咖啡”）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">Carpenter将于下个月踏上英国和欧洲的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">“ Short N&#39;Sweet”之旅</a>，然后今年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535#:~:text=Sabrina%20Carpenter%20has%20been%20announced,for%20BST%20Hyde%20Park%202025.&amp;text=The%20'Espresso'%20singer%20will%20perform,Zach%20Bryan%20and%20Hugh%20Jackman.">在伦敦的BST Hyde Park头条新闻</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xOnTBHWu7xyKRF4SKGSfxVZQUkszki1LzXxF0U0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处找到剩余的门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p>她还将在6月与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">Chappell Roan</a>一起在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera-sound-festival">Primavera Sound</a>的账单中排名第一。</p><p>在其他新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-praises-sabrina-carpenters-new-vogue-cover-3837310">卡彭特（Carpenter）与流行音乐女王（Queen of Pop）的长期摄影师合作，为麦当娜（Madonna）的新<em>Vogue</em>杂志封面赢得了赞誉</a>。</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sabrina-carpenter-and-dolly-partons-new-please-please-please-collab-3837970">收听Sabrina Carpenter和Dolly Parton的新“请请请”合作，</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
