s-tours-asia-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>边界是开放的，现场音乐又回来了， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">K-Pop</a>巡回演出周期如火如荼。包括经验丰富的偶像朋友在内的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gfriend">明星</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">十七岁</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/day6">第6天</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hope">J-Hope</a>等人正在以新的和旧的曲调巡回世界 - 很快就会击中亚洲。</p><p>尽管其中一些艺术家正在展开自己的标题节目，但其他艺术家则参加了音乐节的阵容，其中包括多流派和仅Hallyu的阵容。最近的公告越来越快，因此<em>NME</em>决定为2025年在亚洲举行的K-Pop音乐会和音乐节提供方便的清单。</p><p>向下滚动以查看您最喜欢的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">K-Pop</a>艺术家是否正在巡回亚洲，并获取有关城市，约会，场地，门票等的信息。</p><h2> J-Hope </h2><figure id="attachment_3827736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/j-hope-2025-tour-concert-getty.jpg" alt="BTS J-Hope 2025 Tour音乐会门票约会更多" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/j-hope-2025-tour-concert-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/j-hope-2025-tour-concert-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/j-hope-2025-tour-concert-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/j-hope-2025-tour-concert-getty-696x442