r />星期六7  - 中国香港，亚洲 - 艾琳娜</p><p>去年11月，她的第六次独奏迷Mini-Album“给我自己的信”发行后，女子一代领袖和独奏家Taeyeon宣布了她的最新“ The Tense”独奏巡回演出。即将到来的巡回演唱会在今年三月的三月音乐会开始，即将举行的巡回演唱会在2025年上半年在东亚少校和东南亚少校演出，包括台北，马尼拉，新加坡等。</p><h2>蒂芙尼年轻</h2><figure id="attachment_3757143" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3757143" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3757143" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524.jpg" alt="蒂芙尼年轻" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/tiffany-young-newer-idols-170524-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3757143" class="wp-caption-text">蒂芙尼年轻。学分：Daniele Venturelli通过Getty。</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>2025年&#39;在这里为您&#39;&#39;粉丝 - 康塞特亚洲巡回演唱会 - 胡志明</strong></p><p><strong>2025年3月</strong><br />星期六22  - 越南何志明（Ho Chi Minh），Nguyen de体育馆</p><p>女子一代歌手蒂法尼（Tiffany）将作为她2025年的“在这里为您”的粉丝concerts进行亚洲巡回演出，其第一站宣布为越南城市Ho Chi Minh。目前尚不清楚她是否计划访问亚洲各地的更多城市。</p><h2>周杰伦b </h2><figure id="attachment_3809176" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809176" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809176" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025.jpg" alt="Got7 Jay B磁带重新加载音乐会2024 2025" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/got7-jay-b-tape-road-concert-2024-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809176" class="wp-caption-text">杰伊·B（Jay B.</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>2025年的“磁带：重载”  - 马尼拉，台北，东京，雅加达和吉隆坡</strong></p><p><strong>2025年3月</strong><br />星期日2  - 马尼拉，菲律宾，1厅SMX会议中心<br />星期日9  - 台北，台湾，台北国际会议中心<br />星期三19  - 日本东京，霍利克·霍尔（售罄）</p><p> <strong>2025年4月</strong><br />星期六5  - 印度尼西亚雅加达，卡萨布拉卡阿鲁巴厅<br />星期日27  - 马来西亚吉隆坡，吉普·卢珀</p><p>GOT7成员和独奏家Jay B宣布了计划于3月和4月举行的五站亚洲之旅，以支持他最近发行的同名专辑。</p><h2>马尼拉炸弹</h2><figure id="attachment_3831673" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831673" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831673" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up.jpg" alt="马尼拉水炸炸弹2025年2月阵容" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-lin